      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Meticulously maintained, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this M3 retains its original factory paint depth and exhibits zero mechanical or cosmetic deficiencies. A purist\u2019s spec with a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline, ready for any collection.",
